<br>
Was in Sleepers the other day, and it would not stick on even Sentries.  I just use my primal 2h now and I hold agro a whole lot better on the Sentries than when using primal warsword and red epic.  Never worked on lizards in CT, but now seems it doesnt stick well on the goos either.  I have been finding my agro control to be alot worse now. Anyone else experiencing this? <br>
<br>
Was talking to a Paladin friend, and he said that the paly epic proc, which I guess is fire based, is hardly resisted anywhere, including lizards in CT.  That just doenst sound right.  Did we get the shaft in the last patch? <br>
<br>
Becker <br>
Warlord of Sojourners<br>
Brell Serellis<br>
